{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867796300,"sessionID":"ses_2860b7265ffe45JshERrf1yicI","part":{"id":"prt_d79f81185001nfxEE2iXyTipt0","messageID":"msg_d79f7eb20001kQCIPu1fjUbT6M","sessionID":"ses_2860b7265ffe45JshERrf1yicI","type":"text","text":"Created comprehensive design.md for AR-022 (CLI publish 命令) at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-022/design.md`\n\nThe design document includes:\n\n- **Architecture**: Component overview with diagrams showing CLI → Runtime → Provider → Platform flow\n- **Implementation Details**: Complete code for Typer command interface, PublishRuntime class, Docker/AgentCube/K8s provider integration\n- **Data Structures**: PublishOptions, DeploymentResult, AgentRuntimeSpec models\n- **Error Handling**: Custom exception hierarchy with handling patterns for Docker, registry, and deployment errors\n- **Testing Strategy**: Unit tests and integration tests with fixtures\n- **Configuration**: Environment variables and config file examples\n- **Security**: Registry authentication, RBAC, network security considerations\n- **Performance**: Image push optimization, deployment performance metrics\n- **Deployment Strategy**: 5-week phased implementation plan\n- **Appendices**: Complete command reference, example workflows, troubleshooting guide","time":{"start":1775867796298,"end":1775867796298}}}
